[[File:Anna_Maria_Bisi.jpg|thumb|right|A. M. Bisi]] '''Anna Maria Bisi''' (1938–1988), known as '''A. M. Bisi''', was an Italian [[archaeologist]] and academic, specialising in the [[Phoenicians]] and [[Punics]].
==Life== Bisi had a single minded career. She was supported by S.Moscato when she obtained her doctorate and after she published "Il grifone: dalle origini orientali al VI secolo a.C.” in 1965 and two years later “Le Stele puniche,” again in "Studi Semitici" but this time on Punic archaeology.<ref name="Breaking"/> Bisi was made [[Professor]] of Punic Antiquities at the [[Sapienza University of Rome]] in 1969, and Professor of the Archaeology of the [[Ancient Near East]] at the [[University of Urbino]] in 1971. Her research focused on [[artisanal handicrafts]] and [[iconography]], through which she studied the spread of Phoenician culture and [[cultural relations]] throughout the Mediterranean.<ref name="Breaking">{{cite web|last1=Dolce|first1=Rita|title=Anna Maria Bisi|url=https://www.brown.edu/Research/Breaking_Ground/bios/Bisi_Anna%20Maria.pdf|website=Breaking Ground: Women in Old World Archaeology|publisher=Brown University|accessdate=3 April 2018|format=pdf}}</ref><ref name="Old">{{cite web|title=Anna Maria Bisi|url=https://www.brown.edu/Research/Breaking_Ground/results.php?d=1&first=Anna%20Maria&last=Bisi|website=Women in Old World Archaeology|publisher=Brown University|accessdate=3 April 2018}}</ref><ref name="obit">{{cite journal|last1=Gilbert|first1=Charles-Picard|title=Anna-Maria Bisi (1938-1988)|journal=Antiquités africaines|date=1991|volume=27|issue=1|page=13|url=http://www.persee.fr/doc/antaf_0066-4871_1991_num_27_1_1180|accessdate=3 April 2018|language=French}}</ref>
==Selected works== * {{cite book |last1=Moscati |first1=Sabatino |authorlink= Sabatino Moscati |last2=Bisi |first2=Anna Maria |title=Storia universale dell'arte |date=1989 |publisher=UTET |location=Torino |isbn=978-8802042381 |language=Italian}} * {{cite book |last1=Bisi |first1=Anna Maria |title=Le terrecotte figurate fenicie e puniche in Italia |date=1990 |publisher=Libreria dello Stato, Istituto poligrafico e Zecca dello Stato |location=Rome |isbn=978-8824001106 |language=Italian}}
